These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-1::.
7 different games are played: mah-jongg, scrabble, whist, bridge, monopoly, backgammon, snooker
House: modern, townhouse, tower, cape-cod, victorian, ranch-style, art-deco
 1. the tower house is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 2. the tower house is on the right of the victorian house##1
 3. the tower house is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
 4. the art-deco house is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 5. the townhouse house is the person playing bridge##1
 6. the modern house is in the middle##1
 7. the cape-cod house is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person playing whist is in an even position##4
 9. the ranch-style house is in an odd position##4
10. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
11. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
12. the person playing whist is the victorian house##1
13. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
14. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |    7    |
| Game   | monopoly      | whist      | backgammon    | snooker    | scrabble | mah-jongg     | bridge     |
| House   | cape-cod | victorian | tower | modern | ranch-style   | art-deco | townhouse |

