.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: classical, d&b, dubstep, techno, blues, funk, metal
There are 7 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, juice, fanta, almond-milk, mirinda, iced-tea
 1. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 2. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
 4. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 5. the fan of blues is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person drinking mirinda is the fan of techno##1
 7. the fan of d&b is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 8. the fan of funk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 9. the fan of techno is the person drinking mirinda##1
10. the fan of dubstep is between the person drinking mirinda and the fan of d&b##2
11. the fan of funk is in the middle##1
12. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
13. the fan of d&b is on the far left or far right##3
14. the fan of metal is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |    3    |     4      |      5      |     6     |   7    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b   | dubstep | techno | funk   | metal | classical | blues |
| Beverage           | almond-milk | cola          | mirinda    | sprite | fanta     | juice      | iced-tea    |

