7 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, davidoff, montecristo, fonseca, ritmeester, old-henry, siglo
 1. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
 2. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
 3. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the pall-mall-smoker##3
 4. the townhouse house is between the art-deco house and the ranch-style house##2
 5. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the davidoff-smoker##3
 6. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 7. the ritmeester-smoker is in an odd position##4
 8. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far left##1
 9. the davidoff-smoker is the colonial house##1
10. the colonial house is on the far right##1
11. the old-henry-smoker is the cottage house##1
12. the ritmeester-smoker is between the futuristic house and the cottage house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |       5        |        6        |     7      |
| House   | ranch-style        | townhouse  | art-deco | futuristic | modern           | cottage           | colonial  |
| Cigar    | pall-mall | fonseca | siglo   | montecristo    | ritmeester | old-henry | davidoff |

