There are 7 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, coffee, cola, fanta, 7up, lemonade
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
 2. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the owner of the hamster is in an even position##4
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 7. the person drinking cola is in an odd position##4
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
11. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
12. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left##1
13. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4      |      5       |      6      |      7      |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | snake    | ferret | hamster | mouse      | dog | rabbit |
| Beverage     | lemonade  | almond-milk | cola   | coffee  | 7up | fanta     | hot-chocolate    |

