.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-19::.
7 different games are played: poker, go, snooker, billiard, scrabble, bridge, chess
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, dannemann, prince, cain, pall-mall, blend, bluemaster
 1. the person playing go is the blend-smoker##1
 2. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
 3. the pall-mall-smoker is the person playing chess##1
 4. the bluemaster-smoker is the person playing bridge##1
 5. the pall-mall-smoker is in the middle##1
 6. the prince-smoker is on the far right##1
 7. the person playing billiard is in an odd position##4
 8. the person playing scrabble is the prince-smoker##1
 9. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
10. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person playing go##1
11. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
12. the person playing billiard is in an odd position##4
13. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person playing poker##1
14. the cain-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |     5     |    6    |    7    |
| Game          | billiard  | go | poker     | chess  | snooker | bridge    | scrabble  |
| Cigar   | cain | blend  | fonseca | pall-mall | dannemann | bluemaster | prince |

