.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-20::.
7 different games are played: go, scrabble, bridge, poker, domino, backgammon, whist
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: surfing, volleyball, sailing, basketball, golf, snowboarding, parkour
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
 2. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
 3. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
 4. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
 5. the person playing poker is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 7. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 8. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is in an odd position##4
10. the person playing whist is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
11. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
12. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |   5    |      6      |    7     |
| Game          | backgammon   | bridge | whist | go | domino | scrabble | poker |
| Sport   | golf | parkour      | snowboarding     | sailing  | basketball | surfing         | volleyball    |

 